Follow this title schema when clear:
{{.TitleSchema}}

Schema meaning:
- sender: full person, company, or institution name
- document_type: broad reusable kind, not list/overview wording
- reference: invoice, delivery note, contract, customer, account, or case number
- subject: short distinguishing detail

Rules:
- Language is likely {{.Language}}.
- Do not prefix dates; Paperless stores dates separately.
- Put domain/category details in the subject only when needed for clarity.
- Avoid repeating domains already captured by tags or Paperless metadata.
- Respond only with the title.

